<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
       font-family: Segoe UI; 
      }
      .container {
        padding: 30px;
        height: fit-content;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0px 0px;
      }
      .container-success {
        background: #B7F5D280;
        border-top: 5px solid #4BCA81;
      }
      .container-warning {
        background: #fcf3e0;
        border-top: 5px solid #d79301;
      }
      .container-reminder {
        background: #B7DFF5;
        border-top: 5px solid #1178B1;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
        background: white;
      }
      .details-box {
        border: 1px solid #C9C9C9;
      }
      .padding-left-right-small {
        padding: 0px 20px;
      }
      .horizontal-bar {
        height: 1px;
        background: #C9C9C9;
      }
      .table-container td{
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .scheduled-time-cell {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .margin-right-xx_small {
        margin-right: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
            <div class="container container-success">
            <div class="content">
            <p>
            שלום, {!Lead.Name},
            </p>
            <p>
            ‏פעילות השירות עם <b>{!ServiceResource.Name}</b> נקבעה למועד אחר.</b>
            </p>
            <div class="details-box">
            <p class="padding-left-right-small">
            הנה הפרטים:
            </p>
            <div class="horizontal-bar"></div>
            <div class="table-container">
            <table>
            <tr>
            <td>
            מועד:
            </td>
            <td class="scheduled-time-cell">
            <img src="https://test.salesforce.com/img/icon/t4v35/utility/event_60.png" height="15" class="margin-right-xx_small">
            <b>{!DATETIMEVALUE(ServiceAppointment.SchedStartTime)} - {!DATETIMEVALUE(ServiceAppointment.SchedEndTime)} ({!User.TimeZoneSidKey})</b>
            </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td>
            נושא הפגישה:
            </td>
            <td>
            <b>{!ServiceAppointment.WorkType}</b>
            </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td>
            פגישה עם:
            </td>
            <td>
            <b>{!ServiceResource.Name}</b>
            </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td>
            סוג הביקור:
            </td>
            <td>
            <b>{!ServiceAppointment.AppointmentType}</b>
            </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
            <td>
            מחיר:
            </td>
            <td>
            <b>[CURRENCY] [AMOUNT]</b>
            </td>
            </tr>
            </table>
            </div>
            </div>
            <p>
            אם שינית את דעתך, ניתן <a target="_blank" href="[[MODIFY_APPT_FLOW_URL]]">לשנות או לבטל</a> את פעילות השירות שלך.
            </p>
            </div>
            </div>
          </body>
</html>